[SN]TITLE[SN]
IPL decision sets social media abuzz

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
News of the suspension of two top Indian Premier League teams over a corruption scandal has set Indian social media users abuzz.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Many welcomed the news of the panel's ruling, saying it would restore the trust of millions of cricket fans.
Many called for more to be done to clean up the sport.
But there were others who feared that illegal betting and match-fixing would continue.
